description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Whole Body Pilates' from the channel Christie Wang.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Groove Session and The Zen Flow vibe.
The The Groove Session vibe means Fun, fluid, expressive, completely in the moment. This is especially good for Days when you want to move intuitively and just vibe. The The Zen Flow vibe means Grounding, intentional, breath-centered, unhurried. This is especially good for When you need balance, mindfulness, and release..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Work through whole body pilates exercises with Christie and Nick from Seville on this rainy day. ...
